c7","tid":1458333,"uid":41343,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:05:45.000Z","msg":"#9169, #9170<br />\n&lt;HA Secrets admin 們現正澄清, 傷者眼球被警方布袋彈射中&gt;<br />\n請問關於811 right eye burst case, HA有冇權利出聲明否認/ 制止網上流傳自稱護士/FA所寫既謠言？ Under HA's patient privacy policy, 至少HA employee 係一定唔可以公開病人資料（除非有patient consent)，何況係假消息！！<br />\n<br />\nAdmin: 佢班友點會出黎, 等admin 黎啦 !<br />\n篇野係諗過先打, 話未fact check 扮晒 hearsay 甘去徊避所有patient privacy 問題. HA 係有責任去澄請正確既治療同檢查. d 人睇得cctvb多 , 以為槍傷一定係甘既樣.   <br />\n<br />\n而寫依篇野既人, 甘樣消費傷者, 實在冇恥. 因住天收. <br />\n<br />\n#9170 眼科醫生回應regina leung 嘅comment<br />\n<br />\n以眼科角度黎講，根據該病人受傷位置，係唔會照X-Ray，而係會照CT brain + face.<br />\n因為我哋要睇有冇傷及個腦，眼骨，面骨同埋有冇眼內異物（intraocular foreign body)。而做X-ray係對於診斷呢啲情況嘅sensitivity係太低。XRay 都幫唔到我地去處理個病，因為只有CT先可以講到啲骨點裂發同埋眼內異物嘅位置。<br />\n<br />\n所以無人會照XRay。照左係會被人恥笑。"},{"pid":"ad17726049e5a32df7ac97641e886e052ea33670","tid":1458333,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:07:00.000Z","msg":"Sorry ching 借位<br />\n<br />\n突發！ 816攬炒啦你老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456799\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456799</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"722421f163aae354957a778f2d1771c126fcf45f","tid":1458333,"uid":139450,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLX3Tch.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLX3Tch.png&h=88bd8efb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nedit左 變左消息有待認證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab4cd69996c3c774fc7b93b63703391971ee79f","tid":1458333,"uid":98431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:13:25.000Z","msg":"布袋彈同槍只有警察會配備<br />\n<br />\n除非有魔警私自流出市面 支持成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n還警察公道!"},{"pid":"44452746be6c74dcabe52051ed89d07b3829ba2e","tid":1458333,"uid":53258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"722421f163aae354957a778f2d1771c126fcf45f","tid":1458333,